== Negation ==
Negative particle ن ‹na-› takes the stress and prefixes conjugated verb, not the invariant part

== Negative copula ==
* {{Persian/text|نیستم|nistam|I am not}}
* {{Persian/text|نیستید|nistid|you are not}}
* {{Persian/text|نیست|nist| he/she/it is not}}, colloquially pronounced ‹nis›
* {{Persian/text|نیستیم|nistim| we are not}}
* {{Persian/text|نیستید|nistid|you are not}}
* {{Persian/text|نیستند|nistand|they are not}}, colloquially pronounced ‹nistan›

== Other negative words ==
*{{term-fa|هیچ|hic|none, not at all}}

<br style="clear:both" />

